msgid "The \"nested groups\" options are advanced options for queries that do not have any specific condition at the base of the query. Use Add nested \"or\" condition groups if you need to build a query of the form. (a or b) and (c or d) [or (e and f)..]"
msgstr "“嵌套组”选项是针对基础条件为空的高级查询选项。如果需要构建类似 (a 或 b) 且 (c 或 d) [或 (e 且 f)..] 的查询，请使用“添加嵌套【或】条件组”。"

msgid "Add nested \"or\" condition groups"
msgstr "添加嵌套的“或”条件组"

msgid "Use Add nested \"and\" condition groups if you need to build a query of the form (a and b) or (c and d) [or (e and f)..]"
msgstr "如果需要构建类似 (a 且 b) 或 (c 且 d) [或 (e 且 f)..] 的查询，请使用“添加嵌套【且】条件组”。"

msgid "Add nested \"and\" condition groups"
msgstr "添加嵌套的“与”条件组"

msgid "Currently querying for ALL candidates."
msgstr "当前正在查询所有受试者。"

msgid "You can add conditions by clicking one of the buttons below."
msgstr "您可以通过单击下方的按钮之一来添加条件。"

msgid "Click Add Condition to add one or more conditions to your filters (ie. \"Date Of Birth < 2015-02-15\"). This is most likely where you want to start your filters."
msgstr "单击“添加条件”可向过滤器添加一个或多个条件（例如 “出生日期 < 2015-02-15”）。这通常是您开始设置过滤器的地方。"

msgid "You can also import a population from a CSV by clicking the Import from CSV button."
msgstr "您还可以通过单击“从 CSV 导入”按钮从 CSV 文件导入受试群体。"

msgid "The advanced options are for queries that do not have a condition to add at the base of the query."
msgstr "高级选项适用于在查询基础层级无需添加任何条件的查询。"

msgid "Add Condition"
msgstr "添加条件"

msgid "Import from CSV"
msgstr "从 CSV 导入"

msgid "Use New \"and\" subgroup if the rest of the query you need to write is a subgroup consisting of \"and\" conditions. ie your query is of the form: (your condition above) or (c and d [and e and f..])"
msgstr "如果查询的其余部分是由“与 (And)”条件组成的子组，请使用“新建【与】子组”。即您的查询形式为：(上述条件) 或 (c 且 d [且 e 且 f..])"

msgid "New \"and\" subgroup"
msgstr "新建“与”子组"

msgid "Use New \"or\" subgroup if the rest of the query you need to write is a subgroup consisting of \"or\" conditions. ie your query is of the form: (your condition above) and (c or d [or e or f..])"
msgstr "如果查询的其余部分是由“或 (Or)”条件组成的子组，请使用“新建【或】子组”。即您的查询形式为：(上述条件) 且 (c 或 d [或 e 或 f..])"

msgid "New \"or\" subgroup"
msgstr "新建“或”子组"

msgid "Currently querying for any candidates with:"
msgstr "当前正在查询符合以下条件的受试者："

msgid "Add \"and\" condition"
msgstr "添加“与”条件"

msgid "Add \"or\" condition"
msgstr "添加“或”条件"

