msgstr "在以下至少一次访视中"

msgid "This field may exist multiple times for a single {{scope}}. Adding a criteria based on it means that it must match for <italic>at least one</italic> of the data points."
msgstr "此字段在单个 {{scope}} 中可能存在多次。基于其添加标准意味着它必须匹配<斜体>至少一个</斜体>数据点。"

msgid "This field may exist multiple times for a single {{scope}} and must match for *any* of the data points"
msgstr "此字段在单个 {{scope}} 中可能存在多次，并且必须与*所有*数据点匹配"

